\par <#/>His mobilisation programme assumes three forms: public sector, formal private sector and the informal private sector developers. <#/>In the public sector housing objective, it is the National Housing Corporation (NHC), the Local Govern
ment Loans Authority (LGLA), together with the Ministry of Lands and Housing, that are the operative agencies responsible for implementing the national housing programme.
\par <#/>A critical report on the public sector housing policy, made available to the }{\i\fs24\lang2057 Standard on Sunday}{\fs24\lang2057 
